From 1f6452c17cbbb3447b744ed3c65a94ea64ae1cef Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Alexander Hoffman <alxhoff@gmail.com>
Date: Thu, 7 Aug 2025 16:01:57 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 18/43] usb: Add Quectel RG255C 5G modem to the option serial
 driver

Add USB product ID for the Quectel RG255C-GL 5G cellular modem to the
option serial driver so that the modem's serial AT-command and data
interfaces are properly enumerated.
---
 kernel/kernel/drivers/usb/serial/option.c | 215 +++++++++++++++++++++-
 1 file changed, 212 insertions(+), 3 deletions(-)

